24static inline isc_result_t
25fromtext_amtrelay(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
26 isc_token_t token;
27 dns_name_t name;
28 isc_buffer_t buffer;
29 unsigned int discovery;
30 unsigned int gateway;
31 struct in_addr addr;
32 unsigned char addr6[16];
33 isc_region_t region;
34
35 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
36
37 UNUSED(type);
38 UNUSED(rdclass);
39 UNUSED(callbacks);
40
41 /*
42 * Precedence.
43 */
44 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
45 false));
46 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU) {
47 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
48 }
49 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
50
51 /*
52 * Discovery.
53 */
54 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
55 false));
56 if (token.value.as_ulong > 1U) {
57 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
58 }
59 discovery = token.value.as_ulong;
60
61 /*
62 * Gateway type.
63 */
64 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
65 false));
66 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0x7fU)
67 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
68 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong | (discovery << 7), target));
69 gateway = token.value.as_ulong;
70
71 if (gateway == 0) {
72 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
73 }
74
75 if (gateway > 3) {
76 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
77 }
78
79 /*
80 * Gateway.
81 */
82 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
83 false));
84
85 switch (gateway) {
86 case 1:
87 if (inet_pton(AF_INET, DNS_AS_STR(token), &addr) != 1) {
88 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADDOTTEDQUAD);
89 }
90 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
91 if (region.length < 4) {
92 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
93 }
94 memmove(region.base, &addr, 4);
95 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
96 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
97
98 case 2:
99 if (inet_pton(AF_INET6, DNS_AS_STR(token), addr6) != 1) {
100 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADAAAA);
101 }
102 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
103 if (region.length < 16) {
104 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
105 }
106 memmove(region.base, addr6, 16);
107 isc_buffer_add(target, 16);
108 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
109
110 case 3:
111 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
112 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
113 if (origin == NULL) {
114 origin = dns_rootname;
115 }
116 return (dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options,
117 target));
118 default:
119 INSIST(0);
120 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
121 }
122}

124static inline isc_result_t
125totext_amtrelay(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
126 isc_region_t region;
127 dns_name_t name;
128 char buf[sizeof("0 255 ")];
129 unsigned char precedence;
130 unsigned char discovery;
131 unsigned char gateway;
132 const char *space;
133
134 UNUSED(tctx);
135
136 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
137 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 2);
138
139 if ((rdata->data[1] & 0x7f) > 3U)
140 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
141
142 /*
143 * Precedence.
144 */
145 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
146 precedence = uint8_fromregion(&region);
147 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
148 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", precedence);
149 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
150
151 /*
152 * Discovery and Gateway type.
153 */
154 gateway = uint8_fromregion(&region);
155 discovery = gateway >> 7;
156 gateway &= 0x7f;
157 space = (gateway != 0U) ? " " : "";
158 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
159 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u %u%s", discovery, gateway, space);
160 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
161
162 /*
163 * Gateway.
164 */
165 switch (gateway) {
166 case 0:
167 break;
168 case 1:
169 return (inet_totext(AF_INET, &region, target));
170
171 case 2:
172 return (inet_totext(AF_INET6, &region, target));
173
174 case 3:
175 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
176 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
177 return (dns_name_totext(&name, false, target));
178
179 default:
180 INSIST(0);
181 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
182 }
183 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
184}

186static inline isc_result_t
187fromwire_amtrelay(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
188 dns_name_t name;
189 isc_region_t region;
190
191 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
192
193 UNUSED(type);
194 UNUSED(rdclass);
195
196 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
197
198 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &region);
199 if (region.length < 2)
200 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
201
202 switch (region.base[1] & 0x7f) {
203 case 0:
204 if (region.length != 2) {
205 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
206 }
207 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
208 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
209
210 case 1:
211 if (region.length != 6) {
212 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
213 }
214 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
215 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
216
217 case 2:
218 if (region.length != 18) {
219 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
220 }
221 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
222 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
223
224 case 3:
225 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, 2));
226 isc_buffer_forward(source, 2);
227 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
228 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options,
229 target));
230
231 default:
232 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
233 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
234 }
235}

237static inline isc_result_t
238towire_amtrelay(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
239 isc_region_t region;
240
241 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
242 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
243
244 UNUSED(cctx);
245
246 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
247 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
248}

250static inline int
251compare_amtrelay(ARGS_COMPARE) {
252 isc_region_t region1;
253 isc_region_t region2;
254
255 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
256 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
257 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
258 REQUIRE(rdata1->length >= 2);
259 REQUIRE(rdata2->length >= 2);
260
261 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
262 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
263
264 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
265}

267static inline isc_result_t
268fromstruct_amtrelay(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
269 dns_rdata_amtrelay_t *amtrelay = source;
270 isc_region_t region;
271 uint32_t n;
272
273 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
274 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
275 REQUIRE(amtrelay->common.rdtype == type);
276 REQUIRE(amtrelay->common.rdclass == rdclass);
277
278 UNUSED(type);
279 UNUSED(rdclass);
280
281 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(amtrelay->precedence, target));
282 n = (amtrelay->discovery ? 0x80 : 0) | amtrelay->gateway_type;
283 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(n, target));
284
285 switch (amtrelay->gateway_type) {
286 case 0:
287 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
288
289 case 1:
290 n = ntohl(amtrelay->in_addr.s_addr);
291 return (uint32_tobuffer(n, target));
292
293 case 2:
294 return (mem_tobuffer(target, amtrelay->in6_addr.s6_addr, 16));
295 break;
296
297 case 3:
298 dns_name_toregion(&amtrelay->gateway, &region);
299 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
300 break;
301
302 default:
303 return (mem_tobuffer(target, amtrelay->data, amtrelay->length));
304 }
305}
306
307static inline isc_result_t
308tostruct_amtrelay(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
309 isc_region_t region;
310 dns_rdata_amtrelay_t *amtrelay = target;
311 dns_name_t name;
312 uint32_t n;
313
314 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
315 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
316 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 2);
317
318 amtrelay->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
319 amtrelay->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
320 ISC_LINK_INIT(&amtrelay->common, link);
321
322 dns_name_init(&amtrelay->gateway, NULL);
323 amtrelay->data = NULL;
324
325 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
326 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
327
328 amtrelay->precedence = uint8_fromregion(&region);
329 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
330
331 amtrelay->gateway_type = uint8_fromregion(&region);
332 amtrelay->discovery = (amtrelay->gateway_type & 0x80) != 0;
333 amtrelay->gateway_type &= 0x7f;
334 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
335
336 switch (amtrelay->gateway_type) {
337 case 0:
338 break;
339
340 case 1:
341 n = uint32_fromregion(&region);
342 amtrelay->in_addr.s_addr = htonl(n);
343 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
344 break;
345
346 case 2:
347 memmove(amtrelay->in6_addr.s6_addr, region.base, 16);
348 isc_region_consume(&region, 16);
349 break;
350
351 case 3:
352 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
353 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &amtrelay->gateway));
354 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
355 break;
356
357 default:
358 if (region.length != 0) {
359 amtrelay->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base,
360 region.length);
361 if (amtrelay->data == NULL) {
362 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
363 }
364 }
365 amtrelay->length = region.length;
366 }
367 amtrelay->mctx = mctx;
368 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
369}
370
371static inline void
372freestruct_amtrelay(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
373 dns_rdata_amtrelay_t *amtrelay = source;
374
375 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
376 REQUIRE(amtrelay->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
377
378 if (amtrelay->mctx == NULL)
379 return;
380
381 if (amtrelay->gateway_type == 3)
382 dns_name_free(&amtrelay->gateway, amtrelay->mctx);
383
384 if (amtrelay->data != NULL)
385 isc_mem_free(amtrelay->mctx, amtrelay->data);
386
387 amtrelay->mctx = NULL;
388}

402static inline isc_result_t
403digest_amtrelay(ARGS_DIGEST) {
404 isc_region_t region;
405
406 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
407
408 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
409 return ((digest)(arg, &region));
410}

437static inline int
438casecompare_amtrelay(ARGS_COMPARE) {
439 isc_region_t region1;
440 isc_region_t region2;
441 dns_name_t name1;
442 dns_name_t name2;
443
444 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
445 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
446 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_amtrelay);
447 REQUIRE(rdata1->length >= 2);
448 REQUIRE(rdata2->length >= 2);
449
450 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
451 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
452
453 if (memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, 2) != 0 ||
454 (region1.base[1] & 0x7f) != 3)
455 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
456
457 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
458 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
459
460 isc_region_consume(&region1, 2);
461 isc_region_consume(&region2, 2);
462
463 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
464 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
465
466 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
467}
